title: Dell Inspiron 8500 8600 90W PA-10 AC Adapter DF266

Also Fits:  D-Series D/Port Replicator PR01X, M109S Projector.

This item ships with a wall power cord that is either three or six feet long depending on our currently available stock.   

This unit may use a three connector or two connector adapter interface depending on our stock - shown is a three connector. We ship many different models with various serial numbers, labels, and cords - but every model is guaranteed genuine Dell and designed to function with the notebook models and port replicators listed above!.
